import { Route, Switch } from "react-router"
import NavBar from "../../components/TravelPlanApp/navbar"
import { Home } from "./Home"


export const TravelPlanRoutes=()=>{
    return(
        <>
        <NavBar/>
        <Switch>
            <Route path="/travelPlan">
                <Home />
            </Route>
        
        </Switch>
        </>
    )
}
